    "long_instructions": "#### Play together again\r\n- Insert [play](#clickable=play-sound-block) blocks into each [play together](#clickable=id:play_sounds_together) block using `i` and `Enter` (_Don't forget to change the sounds!_)\r\n- Run your program using `Space Bar` and Continue when ready\r\n\r\n::: details [**Want to add a _third_ play together?**]\r\n1. Press `i` to Insert\r\n1. Use `↑` `↓` arrow keys to move around the toolbox\r\n1. Press `Enter` to select the [play-together](#clickable=play-sounds-together-block) block\r\n1. Use `↑` `↓` arrow keys to move it around the workspace, then `Enter` to accept the position.\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**💡 How do you change a sound?**]\r\nWith a play block in focus, use the `→` arrow key to highlight the sound name, then `Enter` to open the list. `Tab` through options and press `Enter` to choose a new sound.\r\n:::\r\n",
